## Regression Modeling of Optimal Travel Planning Design 

### This notebook shows how to predict flight's delay time and  figure out the pattern of flight's delay using regression modeling.
###  Using this prediction, flight booking companies can provide optimal travel plans that minimize the risk of missed flights. Such improvements can result in better customer satisfiction and reduced operating cost.
#### Before running this notebook,  "Data Preparation" Notebook needs to be run first.

msg.data:
Regression Modeling of Optimal Travel Planning Design

This notebook shows how to predict flight's delay time and figure out the pattern of flight's delay using regression modeling.

Using this prediction, flight booking companies can provide optimal travel plans that minimize the risk of missed flights. Such improvements can result in better customer satisfiction and reduced operating cost.

Before running this notebook, “Data Preparation” Notebook needs to be run first.

paragraphs.title: Create GLM Model Settings table
paragraphs.text:
%sql
CREATE TABLE GLMR_OT_Setting(
  setting_name  VARCHAR2(30),
  setting_value VARCHAR2(4000));

paragraphs.title: Turn on Automated Data Preparation and GLM Model Feature Selection
Build the GLM Regression Model
paragraphs.text:
%script

declare
  v_xlst dbms_data_mining_transform.TRANSFORM_LIST;
 
BEGIN
  DBMS_DATA_MINING.CREATE_MODEL(
    model_name          => 'GLMR_OT_Model',
    mining_function     => dbms_data_mining.regression,
    data_table_name     => 'OT_T_TABLE',
    case_id_column_name => 'ID',
    target_column_name  => 'ARRDELAY',
    settings_table_name => 'GLMR_OT_Setting',
    xform_list          => v_xlst);
END;

paragraphs.title: Display GLM Model Settings
paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT setting_name, setting_value
  FROM user_mining_model_settings
 WHERE model_name = 'GLMR_OT_MODEL'
ORDER BY setting_name;

msg.data:
SETTING_NAME	SETTING_VALUE
ALGO_NAME	ALGO_GENERALIZED_LINEAR_MODEL
GLMS_CONF_LEVEL	.95
GLMS_DIAGNOSTICS_TABLE_NAME	GLMR_OT_Diag
GLMS_FTR_GENERATION	GLMS_FTR_GENERATION_ENABLE
GLMS_FTR_SELECTION	GLMS_FTR_SELECTION_ENABLE
GLMS_FTR_SEL_CRIT	GLMS_FTR_SEL_ALPHA_INV
GLMS_MAX_FEATURES	1000
GLMS_PRUNE_MODEL	GLMS_PRUNE_MODEL_ENABLE
GLMS_SELECT_BLOCK	GLMS_SELECT_BLOCK_DISABLE
ODMS_DETAILS	ODMS_ENABLE
ODMS_MISSING_VALUE_TREATMENT	ODMS_MISSING_VALUE_AUTO
ODMS_SAMPLING	ODMS_SAMPLING_DISABLE
PREP_AUTO	ON

  FROM user_mining_model_attributes

paragraphs.title: Show Model Features and p-values
paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT feature_expression, coefficient, std_error, test_statistic, p_value, std_coefficient, lower_coeff_limit, upper_coeff_limit
  FROM DM$VDGLMR_OT_MODEL
  where p_value<=0.01
  ORDER BY ABS(coefficient) DESC ;
